{
  "name": "Breath of Earth Justice",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Bukijutsu.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You begin to collect and manifest earth release chakra until it laces the striking portion of your weapon. The earth release chakra  begins to magnify the weight and striking power of your attacks  allowing you crush anything in your path is little difficulty. You  utilize a powerful barrage of strikes from a series of differing angles doing great damage.</p><p>Select one creature you can see within range as you strike with a flurry of weapon attacks followed by manifestations of earth release chakra of your design. Make 2 melee taijutsu attacks using your weapon, dealing your weapons damage + 3d10 earth damage.</p><p>A creature you hit with 2 or more attacks using this jutsu must succeed a Strength saving throw as you disable one of their arms (your choice) on a failed save. A creature with a disabled arm  in this way cannot use that arm to wield weapons, fulfill jutsu hand seals (HS) requirements or grapple for the next minute. A jutsu  which removes conditions cast at B-Rank or higher can restore the disabled arm.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above B-Rank increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the damage by 1d8. </p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
